1945;;Pink String and Sealing Wax;;British;;Robert Hamer;;Googie Withers, Gordon Jackson, Mervyn Johns;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pink_String_and_Sealing_Wax;;The wife of a pub landlord in Victorian Brighton, who is having an affair, wants to rid herself of her abusive husband. To accomplish this she befriends a young man who works in his father's chemist shop and thus has access to poison.